{"tid":1183860,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[新手遊記] 阿吱阿咗摩洛哥+快閃德國","createTime":"2019-06-03T09:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T14:58:52.000Z","uid":225612,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b8bd1cef11c0de377a708cec004b9ef40cffb767","tid":1183860,"uid":225612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:04:17.000Z","msg":"2019年上半年過得有啲一塌糊塗加上儲咗一年錢同襯有少少時間 所以決定係年中去翻一個長少少嘅旅行 洗滌下心靈同埋諗下黎緊下半年嘅方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實只係一個籍口俾我去個旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但點解係摩洛哥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為之前未踏足過非洲 想睇下非洲係點嘅樣 同埋之前機緣巧合之下睇到一個blog介紹摩洛哥 見到有好多靚景同靚建築 就萌生咗呢個念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿吱阿咗咗咁耐 講翻重點 今次主要行程當然係摩洛哥 但因為轉機 所以會有兩日時間係德國<br />\n<br />\n暫定行程:<br />\nDay 1: Hong Kong --&gt; Frankfurt <br />\nDay 2:Frankfurt --&gt;Casablanca<br />\nDay 3: Casablanca --&gt; Marrakech<br />\nDay 4: Marrakech<br />\nDay 5: Marrakech --&gt; Sahara<br />\nDay 6: Sahara<br />\nDay 7: Sahara --&gt; Fez <br />\nDay 8: Fez <br />\nDay 9: Fez --&gt; Chefchaouen<br />\nDay 10: Chefchaouen --&gt; Casablanca<br />\nDay 11: Casablanca --&gt; Frankfurt --&gt; Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n之前旅行一直都想記錄途中發生過嘅人同事 今次終於的起心肝 試下寫遊記<br />\n新手上路 太耐冇寫過字 希望做到多圖多字 如果文筆唔好或者相影得唔好 各位巴絲多多包涵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最重要希望自己可以堅持到完場 唔好爛尾 叫令係2019年年中有翻少少值高興既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df50c0923a8fa722c07cbcec7d0cc9bce608d14","tid":1183860,"uid":195187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:15:40.000Z","msg":"同我前年一樣只係我西班牙轉飛HAHA  真係好正"},{"pid":"dba4