/>\n阿吱阿咗咗咁耐 講翻重點 今次主要行程當然係摩洛哥 但因為轉機 所以會有兩日時間係德國<br />\n<br />\n暫定行程:<br />\nDay 1: Hong Kong --&gt; Frankfurt <br />\nDay 2:Frankfurt --&gt;Casablanca<br />\nDay 3: Casablanca --&gt; Marrakech<br />\nDay 4: Marrakech<br />\nDay 5: Marrakech --&gt; Sahara<br />\nDay 6: Sahara<br />\nDay 7: Sahara --&gt; Fez <br />\nDay 8: Fez <br />\nDay 9: Fez --&gt; Chefchaouen<br />\nDay 10: Chefchaouen --&gt; Casablanca<br />\nDay 11: Casablanca --&gt; Frankfurt --&gt; Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n之前旅行一直都想記錄途中發生過嘅人同事 今次終於的起心肝 試下寫遊記<br />\n新手上路 太耐冇寫過字 希望做到多圖多字 如果文筆唔好或者相影得唔好 各位巴絲多多包涵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最重要希望自己可以堅持到完場 唔好爛尾 叫令係2019年年中有翻少少值高興既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T17:52:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68100353cc318f38eec01b3acfc3c567432873e","tid":1183860,"uid":207618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T17:57:10.000Z","msg":"oh<br />\n本身都期待有更新。。。<br />\n想睇下究竟係點<br />\n可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423749c6d4bc42c5964cd5957e957222800e094f","tid":1183860,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e68100353cc318f38eec01b3acfc3c567432873e","tid":1183860,"uid":207618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T17:57:10.000Z","msg":"oh<br />\n本身都期待有更新。。。<br />\n想睇下究竟係點<br />\n可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T20:51:10.000Z","msg":"咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2339c9de8426fbbc193a949c4b4383cbf53278","tid":1183860,"uid":52962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T22:31:18.000Z","msg":"好值得去，啲沙好靚，makarresh好有特色，仲要個個用英文溝通到"},{"pid":"a20b2cc40fb55e3ff7335dd9c8d9afa34f117c08","tid":1183860,"uid":225612,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:56:58.000Z","msg":"Day 1<br />\n出發<br />\n<br />\n今次搭 Luthansa 夜機 係 Frankfurt 等17個鐘之後再轉機去 Casablanca <br />\n搭夜機可以食埋個飯就岩岩好準備上機<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivLSs0s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivLSs0s.jpg&h=a8814e86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FQM6xVp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFQM6xVp.png&h=63d1b534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不嬲搭長途機都冇乜運仔 今次都唔例外 差唔多坐滿哂人 惟有坐定定12個鐘啦<br />\n一上到機就昏迷 有野食先醒 一套完整嘅戲都冇睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fi1eGP3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFi1eGP3.jpg&h=ceda9109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yim2QJr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYim2QJr.jpg&h=60613d8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一向對食嘅要求都唔奄尖 除左舊西蘭花淋咗啲同個飽硬咗啲之外 整體黎講都唔錯 不過如果有多杯雪糕就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NJsUKeb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNJsUKeb.jpg&h=e0135c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朝早5點幾落機 未出太陽超級凍 差啲以為自己會凍死 不過晨早落機感覺好似賺咗一日咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gasE2PC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgasE2PC.jpg&h=2246a23e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rLSE2OK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrLSE2OK.jpg&h=8ca89659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好耐冇搭過歐洲火車 感覺翻哂<br />\n歐洲嘅火車站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xc2hPwV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXc2hPwV.jpg&h=5e4fda10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n晨早流流食翻個豬扒飽 成條Zeil都冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HZ1KuzO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHZ1KuzO.jpg&h=eb3e3f5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c1Fvp8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc1Fvp8a.jpg&h=c9c5e757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太早連教堂都未開 決定去9 fing 下先 <br />\n好鐘意可以坐係河隔離睇書野餐跑步嘅感覺<br />\n我諗短幾年命都未必換到可以住係歐洲嘅河隔離 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5OJEiNV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5OJEiNV.jpg&h=35963dcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6RSd7v7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6RSd7v7.jpg&h=420a2ddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有鐵橋嘅地方就有情人鎖 毒撚就惟有望住街裡愛人一對對<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  欣賞下啲鎖都開心嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B9j4uLP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB9j4uLP.jpg&h=52b391bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有條小小小彩虹 個天閂咗你對門 總會開翻扇窗俾你 笑完你就俾翻條彩虹你開心下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c5wZvrB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc5wZvrB.jpg&h=3b2d76d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bt4Xg6N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbt4Xg6N.jpg&h=c515aeda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日好似有個消防活動 有好多消防車同消防員 仲有幾棟野出哂煙 有啲消防員去救火<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rmbbUGr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrmbbUGr.jpg&h=d00a1151&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQZ5eF3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQZ5eF3.jpg&h=6f6b44ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LsgCQer.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLsgCQer.jpg&h=84fb8757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMjwUGd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMjwUGd.jpg&h=988226fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UtGbUGi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUtGbUGi.jpg&h=ea72eeee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNPEji6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNPEji6.jpg&h=456d8399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47i5Zja.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47i5Zja.jpg&h=0a329859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歐洲既教堂真係好靚好莊嚴"},{"pid":"e1d434632592717318ff26586d005abcdcd09f4f","tid":1183860,"uid":225612,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:53:11.000Z","msg":"手快快出咗post同埋上星期見到香港咁冇乜心機出遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/STfToS5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSTfToS5.jpg&h=6ef11f60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hXFOjS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hXFOjS.jpg&h=7d115a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tEawayo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtEawayo.jpg&h=09df65fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cu2nhcY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCu2nhcY.jpg&h=d8baadc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後行咗去Kleinmarkthalle  個市集幾多野賣同睇 啲花開得好靚 口痕試左幾條腸 但食咗三條已經好膩 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XvgfCh2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvgfCh2.jpg&h=ea88d0c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFrankfurt 必打卡點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TKXKvFr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTKXKvFr.jpg&h=46e975b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0idqe5W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0idqe5W.jpg&h=6f7d4ae8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PndRaKo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPndRaKo.jpg&h=e60fdaba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入咗一間餐廳食野 最鐘意喺外國既露天位到食野<br />\n諗住黎到德國冇理由唔食腸 點知好似太大份 食到差啲嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n杯蘋果酒都幾特別<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aAHOcYH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaAHOcYH.jpg&h=49f12f88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oYaW6iU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoYaW6iU.jpg&h=6b71627c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zo4XQLH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZo4XQLH.jpg&h=c85b5f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/11/224909_e3edf5fafdd5fde99fb7fc0b9972de2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F11%2F224909_e3edf5fafdd5fde99fb7fc0b9972de2e.jpg&h=06c351ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZKgn1SR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZKgn1SR.jpg&h=7f43d361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歌德故居 <br />\n歌德係度出世 之前曾經係二戰期間被英軍轟炸 之後再修復 <br />\n入面有好多以前生活嘅痕跡 尤其啲杯杯碟碟幾雅緻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XwWy8w7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwWy8w7.jpg&h=2b09f2ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾鐘意個天文鐘 可睇埋太陽月亮黃道十二宮 下面仲有隻熊仔同個馴獸師 當隻熊仔訓左係到 就係要上鏈既時侯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fDy5ZQB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfDy5ZQB.jpg&h=1cec5165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bspFjWF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbspFjWF.jpg&h=1a80ce22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好有聖誕feel 仲試埋個薯仔餅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sxibrBE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsxibrBE.jpg&h=fda14662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外國既水池可以跳埋落去玩 超爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ss3yEYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSs3yEYn.jpg&h=8c314b16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/COGcVwG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCOGcVwG.jpg&h=7cc61fcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n9點幾都未天黑 好似一日有好多時間咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n準備搭飛機去 Casablanca 入戲肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59f39d5db7601d651dcf7a60603a46b7e78c29c","tid":1183860,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:50:17.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"37963c9c4f57946e683acbe7fbb9b88c7bf4ff0b","tid":1183860,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:56:16.000Z","msg":"morocco 正呀 係啲野食好撚唔岩食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=